Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.89,0:01:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.65,0:01:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's love!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.07,0:01:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Otani Atsushi. Second year, class three.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.23,0:01:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.36,0:01:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I'm Kotobuki. First year, class four.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.70,0:01:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Kotobuki Seiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.02,0:01:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.76,0:01:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I've fallen for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.46,0:01:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.37,0:02:08.37,Title,,170,0,0,,Send Forbidden Love Flying!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.53,0:02:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,How shameless.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.12,0:02:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.54,0:02:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really want to go out with Seiko-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.33,0:02:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Shameless.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.33,0:02:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,How could I say no when her eyes were all sparkly like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.30,0:02:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You always say stuff like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.46,0:02:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You say you're acting cool, but maybe you're just indecisive.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.13,0:02:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just taking it out on me because you're not popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.01,0:02:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean I'm not popular?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.81,0:02:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruka confessed to me, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.93,0:02:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't see you as a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.77,0:02:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,She likes me so much, she couldn't control herself and suddenly kissed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.65,0:02:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a sinful man.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.91,0:02:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,All it took was a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.08,0:02:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Gah! Gahara tapachine poke maha buu!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.91,0:03:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.50,0:03:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a shame, huh, Koizumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.84,0:03:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,As Japan is such a small country, compact things have now become a necessity.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.18,0:03:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Cellphones. Digital Cameras. Laptops.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.76,0:03:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.89,0:03:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,MEN!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.51,0:03:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The era of small men has finally arrived!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.35,0:03:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.94,0:03:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,This has all gone straight to his head.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.98,0:03:30.49,Superscript,,0,0,0,,Afternoon\NPhysical Examinations\NIn the Gym
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.78,0:03:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, that idiot has gotten too carried away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.78,0:03:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, any guy kissed by a girl that cute would get a little cocky.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.12,0:03:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.87,0:03:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus, while most girls call Otani cute,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.79,0:03:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,...very few call him cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.38,0:03:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why he's particularly happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.13,0:03:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,She is cute, but she sure is bold.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.97,0:03:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the first time I've ever seen someone kiss right in front of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.68,0:03:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.27,0:04:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Good afternoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.86,0:04:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, the infamous Seiko-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.65,0:04:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You've had your physical examination?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.61,0:04:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.63,0:04:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... sorry for surprising you yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.74,0:04:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You sure are forward, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.70,0:04:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,After seeing Otani-senpai, I just couldn't help myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.83,0:04:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh... I'm getting all weak just remembering it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.06,0:04:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Uh... Seiko-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.31,0:04:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh! Sorry, I lost it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.39,0:04:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,L-Lost it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.80,0:04:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Whenever I think about someone I like, my mind goes blank.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.62,0:04:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And then my body starts moving by itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.90,0:04:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad. This girl is weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.65,0:04:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, about back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.61,0:04:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,...is Otani-senpai angry because I did that all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.28,0:04:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all. He couldn't be happier.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.83,0:05:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.29,0:05:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to try my best from now on!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.37,0:05:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't mind, please help me, okay, Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.37,0:05:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.51,0:05:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks! I'll be counting on you, okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.43,0:05:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Help, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.61,0:05:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That girl seems to use a strange technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.49,0:05:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Technique?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.57,0:05:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,A technique to grab guy's hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.16,0:05:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,While she's spacing out, she emits a ton of pheromones.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.93,0:05:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Pheromones, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.41,0:05:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a substance that doesn't exist within my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.13,0:05:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, she's sexy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.84,0:05:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,GYOOO! Bupe pubupere bupepre pe zo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.71,0:05:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, she might not even be Otani-kun's type...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.43,0:06:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,...but he was probably caught by all those pheromones.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.27,0:06:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Risa, you give it your best too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.44,0:06:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do I have to give it my best?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.63,0:06:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And just what am I giving my best for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.51,0:06:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Risa-chan, Risa-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.15,0:06:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,WHAT?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.03,0:06:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh... s-sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.32,0:06:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You're helping with the physicals aren't you, Chiharu-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.95,0:06:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay. Risa, have your height measured already.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.42,0:06:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That Seiko-chan is small and cute...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.88,0:06:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Otani's probably happier that someone like her likes him, rather than a giant like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.76,0:06:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Not like I'd ever admit that to anyone, though!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.03,0:06:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Risa-chan, 1...172cm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.39,0:06:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.64,0:06:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,172cm?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.44,0:06:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Ri-Risa-chan... your eyes are scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.15,0:06:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You're lying, right, Chiharu-chan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.53,0:06:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You're lying, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.82,0:06:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Something is definitely wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.82,0:07:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Risa, come back to reality!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.20,0:07:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.53,0:07:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I was definitely 170cm last year!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.45,0:07:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You definitely made a mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.29,0:07:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Measure me again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.74,0:07:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,1...172?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.59,0:07:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.67,0:07:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Two centimeters...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.18,0:07:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I grew another two centimeters...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.30,0:07:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.97,0:07:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And what about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.22,0:07:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen and be amazed...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.31,0:07:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I grew two millimeters!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.06,0:07:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow. I'm amazed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.98,0:07:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You seriously piss me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.15,0:07:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You can gain 2 millimeters just by wearing socks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.53,0:07:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Say whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.28,0:07:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in a good mood today, so I won't let the little things bother me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.82,0:07:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Little pervert.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.12,0:07:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you calling "little pervert"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.54,0:07:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Seiko-chan is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.87,0:07:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Otani-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.66,0:07:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.46,0:07:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Who the heck are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.55,0:07:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You're as cool as always!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.92,0:07:59.17,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.72,0:08:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This is no time to be growing taller, Risa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.93,0:08:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You think I'm doing it on purpose?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.05,0:08:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't do something, Otani-kun and that girl really will get together.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.35,0:08:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Who cares.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.77,0:08:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,He can do what he likes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.10,0:08:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.98,0:08:16.69,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Bye bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.82,0:08:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.16,0:08:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It was your fault for spacing out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.32,0:08:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What if I'd hit my chin and ended up with a big split in it like some foreigner?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.19,0:08:32.06,Superscript,,0,0,0,,MEMO
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.87,0:08:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be handy. You'd be able to stick memos in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.00,0:08:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.66,0:08:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,If you ruin this manly face Seiko-chan will be sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.84,0:08:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure are a happy guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.82,0:08:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.18,0:08:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.59,0:08:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I really like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.26,0:08:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, is that so.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.18,0:08:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,With this charm from the giant goddess, maybe I'll grow taller too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.39,0:08:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The Giant Goddess?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.27,0:08:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Allow me to explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.40,0:08:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,She is known as Koizumi Risa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.94,0:09:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Although she appears to be an ordinary human,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.03,0:09:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,...she is actually the giant goddess from the land of the giants.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.24,0:09:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Who the hell is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.05,0:09:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I really like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.92,0:09:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.34,0:09:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.81,0:09:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem to be in a pretty good mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.85,0:09:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You think so? I'm not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.41,0:09:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! How cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.44,0:09:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Otani-senpai is really cool, isn't he!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.19,0:09:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Over here, over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.99,0:09:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your best, Otani-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.66,0:09:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Otani! Ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.16,0:09:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Owww!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.63,0:09:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.17,0:10:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Otani-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.72,0:10:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay? I'll take you to the infirmary!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.29,0:10:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? Se-Se-Seiko-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.39,0:10:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Otani, who's that cute girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.89,0:10:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Your girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.31,0:10:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? It's not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.44,0:10:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe in the future, though!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.03,0:10:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,This is dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.03,0:10:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Stuck in the infirmary with a devilish woman who doesn't care what others think...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.20,0:10:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,...and has a tendency to kiss suddenly?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.66,0:10:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The {\i1}infirmary{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.20,0:10:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Senpai, don't you think it's hot in here?"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.21,0:10:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And then Seiko slowly undoes her buttons, one by one...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.71,0:10:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.26,0:10:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Na...Nakao-senpai! I remember now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.72,0:10:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That girl seems really cute, right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.31,0:10:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But everyone gets fooled by that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.77,0:11:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She says she doesn't like her real name,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.32,0:11:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...so she tells everyone her name is "Kotobuki Seiko."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.32,0:11:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think it's hot in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.41,0:11:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Otani!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.04,0:11:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But her real name is Kotobuki Seishiro.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.16,0:11:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's actually a guy!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.06,0:11:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,O...Otani?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.94,0:11:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The sports festival is coming up soon, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.40,0:11:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I think the cheer squad is recruiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.82,0:11:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I think I'll sign up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.91,0:11:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're signing up, I-I'll sign up too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.12,0:11:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What does the cheer squad do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.58,0:12:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ch-Cheer, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.49,0:12:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What's so funny, you guys?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.70,0:12:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? What's wrong? You're so upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.72,0:12:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop that snickering!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.68,0:12:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't hold it in anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.14,0:12:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Nobu-chan! I've been holding it in this whole time!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.18,0:12:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna hit you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.02,0:12:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna hit all of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.06,0:12:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Otani. This kind of thing happens all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.73,0:12:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,How can this kind of thing happen all the time?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.74,0:12:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's taken years off my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.16,0:12:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys! Stop laughing! Seriously!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.49,0:12:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,How unfortunate, Otani.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.58,0:12:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But for some reason, I feel relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.67,0:12:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I thinking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.63,0:12:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.26,0:12:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to go watch basketball practice again today?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.55,0:12:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is a boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.46,0:13:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? So you really do like Otani-senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.52,0:13:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No! It's not like I'm going to watch Otani.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.09,0:13:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just keeping Nobu-chan company while she waits for her boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.78,0:13:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But you gave him a wristband as a present, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.78,0:13:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,A wristband?! This is the first I've heard of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.12,0:13:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't give something like that to someone you didn't like right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.50,0:13:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.66,0:13:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,...if a girl as tall as me liked someone as short as Otani, it'd be weird, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.17,0:13:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.63,0:13:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really think that matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.56,0:13:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.18,0:13:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, if that were the case, isn't it even more weird for me to like Otani-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.68,0:13:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.31,0:13:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But Seiko-chan, you don't look like a boy at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.94,0:13:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's not Seiko-chan. It's Seishiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.82,0:13:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Seiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.28,0:13:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.74,0:13:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never thought of myself as a boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.70,0:14:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure God just put me in the wrong body.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.50,0:14:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.49,0:14:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,...did Otani-senpai say anything about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.42,0:14:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Since that day in the infirmary, I feel like he's been avoiding me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.64,0:14:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Does he think I'm disgusting?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.21,0:14:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... I think he's just confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.31,0:14:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.40,0:14:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I'm sure everything will work out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.44,0:14:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.20,0:14:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I had no idea you liked him, and asked you to help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.48,0:14:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, that's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.16,0:14:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,From now on, we're rivals.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.66,0:14:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, no... Like I said...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.25,0:14:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But, I'm not going to lose to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.62,0:14:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll use my charm and pheromones to make Otani-senpai fall for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.17,0:14:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,S-So dazzling!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.60,0:14:57.58,Superscript,,0,0,0,,Sparkle
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.58,0:14:58.58,Superscript,,0,0,0,,Sparkle
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.58,0:14:59.58,Superscript,,0,0,0,,Sparkle
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.58,0:15:00.54,Superscript,,0,0,0,,Sparkle
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.54,0:15:01.28,Superscript,,0,0,0,,Sparkle
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.54,0:15:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Sparkle! Sparkle! Sparkle!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.57,0:15:01.13,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Seiko is so dazzling! Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.19,0:15:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't give something like that to someone you didn't like, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.04,0:15:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You're slouching.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.29,0:15:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.67,0:15:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez, Risa, you're too concerned about your height.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.76,0:15:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only 2cm, yet you're this depressed about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.72,0:15:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Only 2cm? It's a big problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.35,0:15:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know why it's a big problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.89,0:15:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be because...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.10,0:15:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,...you've fallen for a guy who's shorter than you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.28,0:15:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,A guy who's shorter than me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.78,0:16:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Otani-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.42,0:16:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.28,0:16:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I came to play with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.20,0:16:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,No, what's with that outfit?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.33,0:16:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I joined the sports festival cheer squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.17,0:16:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We decided on cheer girl uniforms!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.67,0:16:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheer girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.99,0:16:19.16,Superscript,,0,0,0,,Cheer girl
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.16,0:16:22.58,Superscript,,0,0,0,,Cheer
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.49,0:16:22.58,Superscript,,0,0,0,,Girl
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.51,0:16:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.88,0:16:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheer GIRL?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.76,0:16:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it was super cute, so I had to show you right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.35,0:16:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Cute, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.02,0:16:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.23,0:16:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,A guy falling for another guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.77,0:16:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That would make things really difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.48,0:16:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But he's trying so hard...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.11,0:16:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,...and he's so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.74,0:16:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile I'm sitting here worrying about our height difference...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.91,0:16:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,...keeping my own feelings hidden.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.54,0:16:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Risa,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.96,0:16:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,...let's join the cheer squad too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.25,0:16:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheer girls are totally cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.75,0:16:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Say what?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.17,0:17:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for your hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.47,0:17:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Seiko-chan, you'll be in the same squad as us right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.35,0:17:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Otani-senpai will be with us too, so I'll do my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.02,0:17:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, why do you like Otani-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.86,0:17:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't you prefer someone stronger and more manly?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.44,0:17:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I think Otani-senpai is really manly and cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.49,0:17:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The way he helped me on my first day was just amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.79,0:17:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And also...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.71,0:17:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Height isn't an issue so you can join even if you're short.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.96,0:17:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,...I figured Otani-senpai would be able to accept me wholeheartedly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.55,0:17:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.27,0:17:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,He is a nice guy, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.23,0:17:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,He is, isn't he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.85,0:17:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Otani-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.01,0:17:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh! Hey, stop that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.44,0:18:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Let go, you! Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.98,0:18:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, stop that! Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.86,0:18:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobu-chan, I'll be going on ahead, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.20,0:18:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.41,0:18:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you really a guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.08,0:18:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.58,0:18:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're not really going out with Otani-kun, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.46,0:18:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.34,0:18:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But I do like Otani-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.92,0:18:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I see. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.17,0:18:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.22,0:18:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,See, they can't be going out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.14,0:18:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Otani wouldn't date a huge girl like that, after all.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.56,0:18:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.06,0:18:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean "they can't be going out?!"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.86,0:18:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.23,0:18:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you say such rude things without knowing how hard other people are trying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.32,0:18:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai! Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.07,0:18:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine. It doesn't bother me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.45,0:18:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Seiko-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.50,0:18:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But they were so rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.33,0:18:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.92,0:18:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You think?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.77,0:19:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really think they were...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.17,0:19:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But... now that you mention it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.22,0:19:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,...it's making me sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.60,0:19:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's weird, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.14,0:19:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It really is weird, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.69,0:19:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Me saying that I like Otani-senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.52,0:19:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,N-Not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.44,0:19:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But, even if I confess to Otani-senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.74,0:19:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,...I'll just be laughed at like before.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.28,0:19:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,He thinks I'm disgusting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.37,0:19:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That must be it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.25,0:19:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.33,0:19:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.21,0:19:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.38,0:19:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Otani-senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.43,0:19:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Otani?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.93,0:19:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll say this, at least. I don't hate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.08,0:19:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And I don't think you're disgusting either.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.52,0:20:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you want me to be your boyfriend, that might be a bit of a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.27,0:20:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... What to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.61,0:20:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Ch-Cheer girls are kinda cute, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.12,0:20:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Otani-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.87,0:20:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, stop that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.45,0:20:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I still visit your classroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.64,0:20:21.92,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes! Just let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.04,0:20:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll visit every day in my cheer uniform!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.28,0:20:24.99,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.87,0:20:28.84,Sign,,0,0,0,,12th ANNUAL MAIDO HIGH SPORTS FESTIVAL
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.05,0:20:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.93,0:20:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I said no!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.30,0:20:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.01,0:20:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The girls in our squad will be wearing boys' uniforms,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.64,0:20:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,...and the boys will be dressed as cheer girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.85,0:20:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yeah, that's right...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.27,0:20:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Unlike me, you're a girl Koizumi-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.74,0:20:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You really could become his girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.16,0:20:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're always so concerned about height, you won't find love.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.79,0:21:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your best, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.21,0:21:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I think I'm going to try being a bit more honest.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.34,0:21:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Got you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.89,0:21:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go! What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.56,0:21:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He fits snugly in my arms.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.31,0:21:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey! Wh-Wh-What do you think you're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.82,0:21:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It doesn't matter if I can carry him in my arms.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.78,0:21:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It doesn't matter if he's shorter than me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.28,0:21:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.78,0:21:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...like Otani.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.24,0:21:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,He's being carried!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.20,0:21:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Like a princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.04,0:21:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, let's put him in a cheer girl uniform!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.50,0:21:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Put me down! Put me down, damm it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.37,0:23:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Koizumi, is there someone you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.24,0:23:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... I... Otani... uh...!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.50,0:23:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure are acting weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.59,0:23:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Lovely Complex ~ Love Com.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.25,0:23:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Next: A Maiden's Determination! Love-Love Confession Plan!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.84,0:23:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Be sure to watch!
